If enough people sincerely and persistently in a right heart deeply cry out to God in coordinated prayer for things WE WILL SEE GOD MOVE as we stay in right relationship with Him. I seek to edify with prayers, memes, quotes from FEEDING TEACHING preachers. God is the WORD. God's Word is a ''seed''--from which the Holy Spirit then activates and grows a true christian. The Word is to ''dwell in us richly" and is to "wash and renew" our minds from the deforming things we are daily exposed to in this world. %%%EDIT: Welcome all who wish to join and post. Please respect the focus of the group. NO HEADLINES, NO POLITICAL, NO NEWS--exceptions for when you seek for us to pray for a situation. I will remove these posts otherwise. Part of the aim here is to get our eyes off the world/headlines and onto CHRIST--who's battle it is...our weapons are mighty to the pulling down of strongholds--PRAYER.
